Marketing Operations
The company markets petroleum products under the principal brands of “Chevron,” “Texaco” and “Caltex” throughout many parts
of the world. The following table identifies the company’s and its affiliates’ refined products sales volumes, excluding
intercompany sales, for the three years ended December 31, 2020.
