employees of the company. Diluted EPS includes the effects of these items as well as the dilutive effects of outstanding stock
options awarded under the company’s stock option programs (refer to Note 20, “Stock Options and Other Share-Based
Compensation,” beginning on page 86). The table below sets forth the computation of basic and diluted EPS:
