and tax credit carryforwards of approximately $1,056, primarily related to various international tax jurisdictions. Whereas some of
these tax loss carryforwards do not have an expiration date, others expire at various times from 2021 through 2034. U.S. foreign tax
credit carryforwards of $10,585 will expire between 2021 and 2030.
